    <string name="settings_walletBackupRefundTransactionExplanation">A refund transaction allows you to claim your bitcoins even if our server vanishes completely.
        The refund transaction is time-locked though, which means that you can only claim you bitcoins after the time-lock has expired. Caution: As soon as the refund transaction is valid (after the time-lock expired),
        instant transactions are no longer possible. Your bitcoins need to be "re-deposited" after the time-lock has expired to allow instant transactions. This will be done automatically by the App, but it is
        possible that instant transactions are not possible if you haven\'t openend the app for a very long time (~3 months). </string>
